parameters: Shall we remove the fence and go inside?

Man in black suit: "This is a host club that's scheduled to open
soon."

Man in black suit: "Until it opens, entry is prohibited to anyone who
isn't staff."
Yui: "Just now, it seemed like there was a Zaidarg's combatant..."
Man in black suit: "Eh? No, no, that can't be possible..."
Yui: "But what I saw just now was definitely..."
Yui: "May I take a look inside?"

Man in black suit: "...No, you can't! We're busy preparing for the
opening!"

Man in black suit: "...It's your fault for poking your nose into
things that don't concern you!"
Zaidarg combatant: "As you wish, I'll let you see inside! Hehehe!"
Yui: "Just as I thought, it was a Zaidarg hideout!"
Yui: "Now that I know, I can't overlook this. Prepare yourself!"

Zaidarg combatant: "Huh? What do you mean prepare yourself! Do you
even understand the situation?"

Yui: "Yes, I do understand. It's you who doesn't seem to grasp the
current situation, isn't it?"

Zaidarg combatant: "For a woman, you've got guts, don't you. Or has
fear driven you mad?"
Pony-Celes: "It looks like you've finally understood the situation!"

Pony-Celes: "Though by the time you've understood, it's already too
late!"
Pony-Celes: "Combatants inside, come out right now!"
Pony-Celes: "Now that I'm here, it's the end for all of you!"
